Subject: Implementation of Cash Management, Staff Operations, and Admin Dashboard

Please implement the following features and modules into the project:

1. Daily Cash Reconciliation:

Add a system to track the daily "Cash in Drawer."

Include fields for "Current Balance" and "Daily Cash Withdrawals/Payouts."

Purpose: To audit daily cash flow and prevent potential fraud.

2. Hardware & Marketing Modules:

Printer Discovery: Add a function to search for and connect to printers.

Promotion Management: Add a module to manage shop promotions and discounts.

3. Protocol Creator (Operational Checklist):

Create a "Protocol Creator" tool to manage shop SOPs.

It should include a daily checklist of tasks that must be completed each day.

4. HR & Admin Dashboard (Role-Based Access):

Admin-Only Features: Create an Admin Dashboard to manage KPIs, Salaries, and Leave/Time-off tracking.

Leave & Attendance System:

Admin View: Full overview of all staff leave and attendance.

Staff View: A shared calendar where employees can see who is on leave and who is working each day. This will help them plan their own leave requests.

5. Shift Management System:

Implement a shift rotation system for a 3-person staff.

The system must support flexible scheduling where staff members rotate pairs or work individual shifts throughout the week.

Please ensure the UI/UX is consistent and that the backend integration for these features is fully wired.